{{ 'dspln-philosophy-page.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }}

<section class="dspln-philosophy-meaning" aria-label="{{ section.settings.heading | escape }}">
  <div class="dspln-philosophy-meaning__inner">
    <img
      class="dspln-philosophy-meaning__mark"
      src="{{ 'dspln-blood-sweat-tears-mark.png' | asset_url }}"
      alt=""
      width="300"
      height="132"
      loading="lazy"
    >
    <h2 class="dspln-philosophy-heading">{{ section.settings.heading }}</h2>
    <div class="dspln-philosophy-meaning__body">
      {{ section.settings.text }}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "DSPLN philosophy meaning",
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "heading",
      "label": "Heading",
      "default": "BLOOD SWEAT & TEARS"
    },
    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "text",
      "label": "Text",
      "default": "<p>The red, white and blue drops not only represents where we come from, but also epitomizes the relentless pursuit of excellence and mastery within a discipline. Each element, blood, sweat, and tears, symbolizes the sacrifices, perseverance, and dedication required to achieve greatness.</p><p><strong>Blood</strong> signifies the physical effort and occasional pain endured in the pursuit of one's goals.</p><p><strong>Sweat</strong> represents the hard work and toil poured into honing skills and pushing boundaries.</p><p><strong>Tears</strong> embody the emotional investment and resilience needed to overcome setbacks and challenges along the journey.</p><p>Together, these elements encapsulate the essence of unwavering determination and commitment to mastery, serving as a powerful emblem of the relentless pursuit of excellence.</p>"
    }
  ],
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "DSPLN philosophy meaning"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
